## {{!linkable_header('Catalog Description')}}

**COMP 550. Algorithms and Analysis.** 3 Credits.  

Welcome to COMP 550 where we will learn about
formal specification and verification of programs,
several techniques of algorithm analysis, and 
examine some problem-solving paradigms.  

Lastly we will survey of selected algorithms.  

This class will be different from most of undergraduate
computer science classes.
COMP 550 requires more mathematical analysis and 
less programming than most computer science classes.

